summary: Can I request a love letter from peter Parker? My name is emma, I have dyed blonde hair and brown eyes. I love everything about...
question: Can I request a love letter from peter Parker? My name is emma, I have dyed blonde hair and brown eyes. I love everything about space and if you get me talking about it I won’t stop. I like seeing the beauty in things and watching the sun set over the mountains. I usually spend my time watching Netflix with a glass of wine if I’m not studying (which takes up most of my time, I’m an astrophysics major). I’m from New York (forest Hills, same as Peter!) and I love to go home every chance I get
answer:
Dear Emma,

        If you’re reading this, then Ned was right and girls will open random letters left for them on their doorstep and I owe him $5. I don’t know why I started with that, but I think it was important to tell you.  I guess if this letter is me being honest with you, I better be upfront with everything.  I know you are, when it comes to the things you love.  Or, I guess, in my case, the person.

         Emma you’ve got stars in your eyes, and I’m not just saying that because you love space.  I mean you see the beauty in everything, and you make others see it too.  You make me try to find it, even when it feels impossible. You make me better, and maybe I’m being selfish, but I don’t want to let you go.  I want to be with you whether we looking towards the sky or just relaxing at home watching Netflix.  I want to do everything with you.

        With any luck, you’re not laughing right now, or worse, think this is incredibly creepy and never want to speak to me again.  But, I just wanted you to know how I felt, and hopefully, you feel the same way.

        - Peter Parker

2/20
